### 1.4 Registry Hash Integrity Upgrade
- Sweep registry gate now supports full SHA-256 directive hashes.
- Backward compatibility is preserved for legacy 16-char hashes.
- New allocations can store `signature_hash_full` while retaining short-hash compatibility checks.

